text: Chupheuʻat keu jih hana phaedah Han soe chupheuʻat lakee bak Tuhan Meulengkan ureueng nyang izin Allah Hingga ‘oh gadoh takot lam ate Jih jitanyong le peue Tuhan peugah Peue roe nyang Neukheun le Tuhan gata Jijaweub sigra beuna that leupah Keubit roe Tuhan Maha manyang that Maha Raya that hana ban peugah
